About

Danish Royal Christian X of Denmark was born Christian Carl Frederik Albert Alexander Vilhelm on 26th September, 1870 in Charlottenlund, Denmark and passed away on 20th Apr 1947 Amalienborg, Copenhagen, Denmark aged 76. He is most remembered for King of Denmark from 1912 to 1947. His zodiac sign is Libra.
